  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Zombie Survival Action shooter, with a little crafting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You start as a simple Human, collecting garbage, and using hack and slash on cockroaches.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Then the Action starts to get harder, as Zombies starts to emerge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you collect more garbage, and kill more enemies, you get more money.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now you can start to buy weapons and buy Cyborgs to fight the Zombies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Then you will Join the 1st Core as a zombie fighter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can select easy, normal or hard in this Single-player FPS.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879270/extras/7527842dee6782bff88cc0d840b59526.poster.avif?t=1748702067\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879270/extras/7527842dee6782bff88cc0d840b59526.webm?t=1748702067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879270/extras/7527842dee6782bff88cc0d840b59526.mp4?t=1748702067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The '1st core' Cyborgs serves as the first defense against the perilous, scary Zombies lurking amidst the heaps of garbage, concealed within the shadows of the sprawling Mega Cities.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>This is a small animation I made in my old bathroom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It has been cleaned a little after this. ;-)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879270/extras/d59742bf0c8704f3f0462d584224b67b.poster.avif?t=1748702067\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879270/extras/d59742bf0c8704f3f0462d584224b67b.webm?t=1748702067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879270/extras/d59742bf0c8704f3f0462d584224b67b.mp4?t=1748702067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I made this Zombie Survival shooter, in about two months.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I teach kids 3d graphics, and simple programming, and they wanted to make a game for Steam, so I just made this fun, little Zombie Shooter...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hope you have fun...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Zombie Survival Action shooter, with a little crafting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You start as a simple Human, collecting garbage, and using hack and slash on cockroaches.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Then the Action starts to get harder, as Zombies starts to emerge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you collect more garbage, and kill more enemies, you get more money.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now you can start to buy weapons and buy Cyborgs to fight the Zombies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Then you will Join the 1st Core as a zombie fighter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can select easy, normal or hard in this Single-player FPS.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879270/extras/7527842dee6782bff88cc0d840b59526.poster.avif?t=1748702067\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879270/extras/7527842dee6782bff88cc0d840b59526.webm?t=1748702067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879270/extras/7527842dee6782bff88cc0d840b59526.mp4?t=1748702067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The '1st core' Cyborgs serves as the first defense against the perilous, scary Zombies lurking amidst the heaps of garbage, concealed within the shadows of the sprawling Mega Cities.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>This is a small animation I made in my old bathroom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It has been cleaned a little after this. ;-)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879270/extras/d59742bf0c8704f3f0462d584224b67b.poster.avif?t=1748702067\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879270/extras/d59742bf0c8704f3f0462d584224b67b.webm?t=1748702067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879270/extras/d59742bf0c8704f3f0462d584224b67b.mp4?t=1748702067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I made this Zombie Survival shooter, in about two months.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I teach kids 3d graphics, and simple programming, and they wanted to make a game for Steam, so I just made this fun, little Zombie Shooter...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hope you have fun...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
